(* Test build for sml-crdt.

   sml-test is a TEST-only dependency: the CRDT library itself is
   dependency-free (see ../lib/.../sml-crdt/sources.mlb), and only the test
   suite needs the property-testing `Prop`. We therefore include the vendored
   sml-test library here, never from the library's own basis.

   Include order matters for the flat Poly/ML `use` model (tools/polybuild):
     1. the vendored sml-test library (defines structure Test, hence Test.Prop);
     2. our own plain-check Harness (no name clash -- sml-test's library
        exports only the Test structure, not a Harness);
     3. the CRDT library under test;
     4. the suite + Poly/ML entry + MLton main shim. *)

$(SML_LIB)/basis/basis.mlb

../lib/github.com/sjqtentacles/sml-test/sources.mlb
../lib/github.com/sjqtentacles/sml-crdt/sources.mlb

harness.sml
test.sml
entry.sml
main.sml
